result.execSummary:
The defendant was charged with both Operating w/ PAC (5th or 6th) [Modifiers: Modifier-Alcohol Conc. (.20-.249)] and OWI (5th or 6th) [Modifiers: General Alcohol Concentration Enhancer]. The defendant was found guilty of Operating w/ PAC (5th or 6th) [Modifiers: Modifier-Alcohol Conc. (.20-.249)] and the other charge, OWI (5th or 6th) [Modifiers: General Alcohol Concentration Enhancer] was dismissed by the court.

  • Janice L. Walker was found guilty of Operating w/ PAC (5th or 6th) [Modifiers: Modifier-Alcohol Conc. (.20-.249)], a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(1)(b).
  • Janice L. Walker was found guilty of Operating While Revoked (Rev due to alc/contr subst/refusal 4th+), an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 343.44(1)(b).
